{"tid":2191595,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【五毛滿天飛】犬儒思想全面進場，連登仔應如何自處？","createTime":"2020-09-06T14:16:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T14:20:24.000Z","uid":88743,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a3510b78fdf39fea61478149e7c5d00c541d486c","tid":2191595,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T14:16:50.000Z","msg":"何謂犬儒？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/犬儒主義\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%E7%8A%AC%E5%84%92%E4%B8%BB%E7%BE%A9&d=uo2GI0poDlFkSsUZ5iwE4hq8xf71D2STVxQEH8iwqLk%3D&h=cac58a1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/犬儒主義</a><br />\n犬儒主義（希臘語：&kappa;&upsilon;&nu;&iota;&sigma;&mu;ό&sigmaf;，英語：Cynicism）是對他人的動機從根本上不信任的一種心理態度。奉行犬儒主義的人通常對其他人<ins><strong>不抱有信仰與希望，同時否定人們將抱負、慾望、貪欲、刺激、功利等作為自己的生活動力（犬儒主義者認為這些都是徒勞）。</strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n遊行無用，勇武無用，連儂牆無用，民意開始逆轉，開始攰，好想死，仲唔散係弱智，仲唔衝係嘥氣，條例已經死亡，警察已經內鬨<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1320298\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1320298</a><br />\n<br />\n================================<br />\n<br />\n1970年，蘇聯KGB特工Yuri Bezmenov叛變（無中譯，Google譯做 尤里&middot;貝茲諾夫），投靠美國，並公開蘇聯情報部門顛覆敵對國家社會嘅方法。<strong><ins>由意志敗壞（demoralisation）開始，令到整個社會感到無助，唔團結，冷感，撕裂，以致崩潰，不戰而敗。呢套理論有學名，叫「顛覆」Subversion，而達到顛覆嘅行爲，就叫做 active measures</ins></strong> / активные мероприятия。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個PO真係神PO<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家認為連登仔應如何自處<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c6540a5f8f930ccb972df5a5461d903c37227b0","tid":2191595,"uid":60977,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T14:18:18.000Z","msg":"理閪你<br />\n門照出"},{"pid":"09d650d18f22bd9fd108d188095f1671450e7909","tid":2191595,"uid":266294,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T14:19:18.000Z","msg":"唔放棄就得"},{"pid":"5894e50a5ca2de702ddb576135cc68b7dd77625c","tid":2191595,"uid":88743,"like":0